                  <p>Degradation of atmosphere in form of oxygen deficiency, particle pollution, 
                    and depletion of ozone layer</p>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                  <h6>Land Degradation</h6>
                  <img src="land_degradation.jfif" style="width:100%; height:150px;" class="img" alt="Land Pollution image">
                  <p>Deterioration of productive capacity of the land is occuring at an alarming rate. It negatively effects the 
                    land utility and leads to lower food production.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                  <h6>Water Degradation</h6>
                  <img src="water_degradation.jfif" style="width:100%; height:150px;" class="img" alt="Water Pollution image">
                  <p>Contamination of rivers, lakes, oceans and other water bodies with harmful substances, making it toxic for
                    human use and leading to interference in natural functioning of ecosystems.</p>
